'''太阳辐射监测卫星一号'''（{{lang-en|SOLRAD 1}}）是集电子监控、[[X射线天文学|太阳X射线]]和[[紫外线|紫外线]]观测功能于一体的[[人造卫星|人造卫星]]，也是[[美國海軍|美國海軍]][[太阳辐射监测卫星|太阳辐射监测卫星]]与[[银河辐射和背景|银河辐射和背景]]计划的第一步，于1960年6月22日发射入轨。太阳辐射监测卫星一号不但是第一颗成功观测太阳[[X射线|X射线]]和第一颗从地球轨道执行监控任务的卫星，还是第一颗与其他功能卫星共同发射的人造卫星。

卫星由[[美国海军研究实验室|美国海军研究实验室]]开发，从许多方面来看相当于美国第一个卫星项目[[先锋计划_(美国)|先锋计划]]的后续。卫星成功完成科学观测任务，持续传送实用数据直至1960年11月，足以判断太阳的正常{{lang|en|X}}射线辐射水平，并确定太阳{{lang|en|X}}射线活动增强与无线电淡出现象有关。

卫星的科学部件还为银河辐射和背景的[[信号情报|电子监控]]部件提供掩护，后者的任务是绘制[[苏联|苏联]]防空雷达网。监控任务同样取得成功，持续运作至1960年9月22日，表明苏联防空雷达网的密度超出预期。地面控制部门于1961年4月关闭太阳辐射监测/银河辐射和背景卫星一号，令其成为历史上首枚远程关闭的卫星。

== 背景 ==
[[File:Transit_2A_and_GRAB_1.jpg|thumb]]

1957年，[[苏联|苏联]]开始部署[[扇歌|扇歌]]火控雷达控制的[[S-75导弹|S-75]][[面對空飛彈|地对空导弹]]，令美国轰炸机侵入苏联领空的危险程度加大。[[美国空军|美国空军]]开始出动电子侦察机在苏联边境附近活动，希望能逐步确定这些雷达的大致方位和各自工作频率。通过这种方法可以提供苏联外围地区的雷达信息，但无法深入内陆。军方还曾尝试通过射电望远镜寻找[[月球|月球]]偶尔反射的苏联雷达信息，但事实证明这种方法不足以解决问题。<ref name="Bamford2007">{{cite book | last = Bamford | first = James | title = Body of Secrets: Anatomy of the Ultra-Secret National Security Agency | url = https://books.google.com.tw/books?id=VqY4Wr3T5K4C&redir_esc=y | year = 2007 | publisher = Knopf Doubleday Publishing Group | isbn = 978-0-307-42505-8 | deadurl = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130308190139/http://books.google.com/books?id=VqY4Wr3T5K4C | archive-date = 2013-03-08 | accessdate = 2020-07-19 }}</ref>{{rp|362}}

1958年3月<ref name="grabnpoppy">{{cite web | publisher = National Reconnaissance Office | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200717230144/https://www.nro.gov/Portals/65/documents/history/csnr/programs/docs/prog-hist-03.pdf | archivedate = 2020-07-17 | deadurl = no | access-date = 2020-07-19 | format = PDF | url = https://www.nro.gov/Portals/65/documents/history/csnr/programs/docs/prog-hist-03.pdf | title = GRAB and POPPY: America's Early ELINT Satellites | last1 = McDonald | first1 = Robert A. | last2 = Moreno | first2 = Sharon K. }}{{PD-notice}}</ref>{{rp|4}}，[[美国海军研究实验室|美国海军研究实验室]]正全力推进旨在为[[美国海军|美国海军]]发射人造卫星的[[先锋计划_(美国)|先锋计划]]（{{lang|en|Project Vanguard}}），实验室工程师里德·{{lang|en|D}}·梅奥（{{lang|en|Reid D. Mayo}}）判断，先锋计划的衍生产物可以用于绘制苏联导弹发射场地图。梅奥曾为潜艇开发反潜飞机躲避系统，可以提前发现飞机雷达信息后规避。该系统体积小巧，机械结构坚固，可以经过改装适应先锋卫星框架。<ref name="Bamford2007" />{{rp|364}}

梅奥将构想告知实验室对策部主任霍华德·洛伦岑（{{lang|en|Howard Lorenzen}}），后者在[[美国国防部|国防部]]游说。梅奥的设想在六个月后获批，代号“告密者”（{{lang|en|Tattletale}}）。<ref name="Bamford2007" />{{rp|364}}1959年8月24日，[[德怀特·艾森豪威尔|德怀特·艾森豪威尔]]同意全力推进该计划<ref name="grabnpoppy"/>{{rp|4}}。

信息遭《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》泄露后，艾森豪威尔取消计划，但在加强安全措施后以新代号“核桃”（{{lang|en|Walnut}}）重启，卫星部件代号“{{lang|en|DYNO}}”<ref name="25th2" />{{rp|140, 151}}，为避免再度泄密，不但监督更严，而且只有“[[必须知晓|必须知晓]]”的人员才能获得信息<ref name="NRO_Poppy_hist">{{cite web | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200517021426/http://www.theblackvault.com/documents/spysatellites/PoppySatellite.pdf | format = PDF | url = http://www.theblackvault.com/documents/spysatellites/PoppySatellite.pdf | title = History of the Poppy Satellite System | date = 2006-08-14 | publisher = [[美国国家侦察局|National Reconnaissance Office]] | accessdate = 2020-07-19 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2020-05-17 }}</ref>{{rp|2}}。此时美国的太空发射不属机密<ref name="eye">{{cite book | last1 = Day | first1 = Dwayne A. | last2 = Logsdon | first2 = John M. | last3 = Latell | first3 = Brian | title = Eye in the Sky: The Story of the Corona Spy Satellites | publisher = Smithsonian Institution Press | location = Washington and London | accessdate = 2020-07-19 | page = [https://archive.org/details/eyeinskystoryofc0000unse/page/176 176] | date = 1998 | isbn = 978-1-56098-830-4 | url = https://archive.org/details/eyeinskystoryofc0000unse/page/176}}</ref><ref name="collier">{{cite encyclopedia | title = Space Science and Exploration | encyclopedia = Collier's Encyclopedia | year = 1964 | publisher = Crowell-Collier Publishing Company | location = New York | page = 356 | oclc = 1032873498}}</ref>，为避免预期目标发现“{{lang|en|DYNO}}”执行电子监视任务，最好能在卫星发射同期执行共享空间联合飞行掩护任务<ref name="Society2010">{{cite book | author = American Astronautical Society | title = Space Exploration and Humanity: A Historical Encyclopedia [2 volumes]: A Historical Encyclopedia | accessdate = 2020-07-19 | url = https://books.google.com.tw/books?id=2ZNxDwAAQBAJ&pg=PA300&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q&f=false | date = 2010-08-23 | publisher = ABC-CLIO | location = Santa Barbara, Calif | isbn = 978-1-85109-519-3 | archive-date = 2020-07-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200719172236/https://books.google.com.tw/books?id=2ZNxDwAAQBAJ&pg=PA300&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q&f=false | dead-url = no }}</ref>{{rp|300}}。

针对太阳[[电磁波谱|电磁波谱]]的研究为发射“{{lang|en|DYNO}}”提供理想掩护机遇。美国海军此前就想确定太阳[[耀斑|耀斑]]是否会导致无线电通信中断<ref name="Society2010" />{{rp|300}}，以及[[紫外线|紫外线]]和[[X射线|X射线]][[辐射|辐射]]辐射对卫星和宇航员究竟有多大危害<ref name="avweek1960a">{{cite magazine | date = 1960-06-20 | title = 'Bonus' Payload Set for Transit 2A Orbit | url = https://archive.aviationweek.com/issue/19600620#!&pid=76 | magazine = Aviation Week and Space Technology | location = New York | publisher = McGraw Hill Publishing Company | access-date = 2020-07-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190109113719/http://archive.aviationweek.com/issue/19600620#!&pid=76 | archive-date = 2019-01-09 | deadurl = no }}{{subscription}}</ref>{{rp|76}}。受[[地球大气层|地球大气层]]阻挡，地面观测站无法获得所需数据。同时，太阳光谱输出无从预测而且波动剧烈，所以亚轨道[[探空火箭|探空火箭]]也不能有效完成观测任务，只有卫星才能持续长时间研究完整的太阳光谱。<ref name="SP100">{{cite book | date = 1966 | title = Significant Achievements in Solar Physics 1958–1964 | location = Washington D.C. | publisher = NASA | oclc = 860060668}}</ref>{{rp|5–6, 63–65}}<ref name="NAP">{{cite book | chapter-url = https://www.nap.edu/read/11299/chapter/8#157 | title = Navy's Needs in Space for Providing Future Capabilities | author = ((Committee on the Navy's Needs in Space for Providing Future Capabilities, Naval Studies Board, Division on Engineering and Physical Sciences, National Research Council of the National Academies)) | chapter = Appendix A: Department of the Navy History in Space | page = 157 | date = 2005 | access-date = 2020-07-19 | publisher = The National Academies Press | location = Washington D.C. | isbn = 978-0-309-18120-4 | doi = 10.17226/11299 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190107015833/https://www.nap.edu/read/11299/chapter/8#157 | deadurl = no | archive-date = 2019-01-07 }}</ref>

[[File:Atmospheric_electromagnetic_opacity.svg|thumb]]，{{lang|en|X}}射线和紫外线，大部分红外光谱也会被大气吸收]]

海军实验室已经在1959年发射[[先锋三号卫星|先锋三号]]形式的专用太阳观测卫星，上有{{lang|en|X}}射线和紫外线探测器，但在[[范艾伦辐射带|范艾伦辐射带]]的背景辐射下已经完全饱和<ref name="SP100" />{{rp|63}}。海军实验室工程师马丁·沃塔（{{lang|en|Martin Votaw}}）带领尚未转移到[[美国国家航空航天局|美国国家航空航天局]]的先锋计划工程师和科学家组成团队，一起根据先锋计划开发{{lang|en|DYNO}}卫星<ref name="Century">{{cite web | url = https://www.nrl.navy.mil/news/releases/nrl-center-space-technology-reaches-century-mark-orbiting-spacecraft-launches | title = NRL Center for Space Technology Reaches Century Mark in Orbiting Spacecraft Launches | last = Parry | first = Daniel | publisher = U.S. Naval Research Laboratory | date = 2011-10-02 | access-date = 2020-07-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190509131115/https://www.nrl.navy.mil/news/releases/nrl-center-space-technology-reaches-century-mark-orbiting-spacecraft-launches | archive-date = 2019-05-09 | deadurl = no }}{{PD-notice}}</ref>。已有两种用途的卫星更名“银河辐射和背景”（{{lang|en|Galactic Radiation And Background}}，简称{{lang|en|GRAB}}），又称“银河辐射实验背景”（{{lang|en|Galactic Radiation Experiment Background}}，简称{{lang|en|GREB}}），同时卫星又以科研用途命名为“太阳辐射监测”（{{lang|en|SOLRAD}}），是太阳辐射（{{lang|en|SOLar RADiation}}）的简称<ref name="25th2"/>{{rp|142, 149}}<ref name="Society2010" />{{rp|300}}。

1960年4月13日，美国在[[子午仪卫星|子午仪1B]]卫星上附加太阳辐射监测卫星[[质量模拟器|质量模拟器]]并一起成功发射<ref name="Society2010" />{{rp|301}}，证明双卫星发射技术已经成熟<ref name="log">{{Cite web | url = http://planet4589.org/space/log/launchlog.txt | title = Launch Log | last = McDowell | first = Jonathan | publisher = Jonathon's Space Report | access-date = 2020-07-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200609173805/http://planet4589.org/space/log/launchlog.txt | archive-date = 2020-06-09 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。同年5月1日，[[弗朗西斯·加里·鲍尔斯|弗朗西斯·加里·鲍尔斯]]驾驶的[[U-2侦察机|U-2侦察机]]在苏联领空被[[1960年U-2击坠事件|击落]]，证明飞机监视十分危险。5月5日，艾森豪威尔总统批准发射太阳辐射监测卫星。<ref name="avweek1998a">{{cite magazine | date = 1998-06-22 | title = NRO Lifts Veil On First Sigint Mission | url = https://archive.aviationweek.com/issue/19980622#!&pid=26 | magazine = Aviation Week and Space Technology | location = New York | publisher = McGraw Hill Publishing Company | access-date = 2020-07-20 | archive-date = 2020-07-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200720034611/https://archive.aviationweek.com/issue/19980622#!&pid=26 | dead-url = no }}{{subscription}}</ref>{{rp|32}}

== 航天器 ==
[[File:SOLRAD1schematic.gif|thumb]]

太阳辐射监测卫星一号的外形和[[先鋒3號|先锋三号]]相似，大致呈球形，直径51厘米，采用六个圆形[[太阳能电池|太阳能电池]]片供电<ref name="NRO_Poppy_hist" />{{rp|10}}，太阳辐射监测卫星一号的质量为19.05公斤<ref name="NRO_Poppy_hist" />，小于23.7公斤的先锋三号<ref name="vanguardnssdc">{{cite web | access-date = 2020-07-24 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200613021853/https://nssdc.gsfc.nasa.gov/nmc/spacecraft/display.action?id=1959-007A | url = https://nssdc.gsfc.nasa.gov/nmc/spacecraft/display.action?id=1959-007A | title = Vanguard 3 | publisher = NASA Space Science Data Coordinated Archive | archivedate = 2020-06-13 }}{{PD-notice}}</ref>。太阳能电池为九个串联起来的[[D电池|D电池]]供电，共计产生12[[伏特|伏特]]电压<ref name="NRO_Poppy_hist" />{{rp|10}}{{rp|10}}和六[[瓦特|瓦特]]功率<ref name="avweek1998a" />{{rp|32}}。

卫星的太阳辐射监测科学元件包括两个[[莱曼阿尔法线|莱曼阿尔法]][[光度计|光度计]]（[[一氧化氮|一氧化氮]][[电离室|电离室]]），用于研究1050至1350[[埃格斯特朗|埃格斯特朗]]波长范围的紫外线；还有一个{{lang|en|X}}射线光度计（氩电离室），可研究2至8埃格斯特朗波长范围的{{lang|en|X}}射线，这些设备都安装在卫星[[赤道|赤道]]周围<ref name="Instrument">{{cite web | url = https://nssdc.gsfc.nasa.gov/nmc/experiment/display.action?id=1960-007B-01 | title = SOLRAD 1 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200615005757/https://nssdc.gsfc.nasa.gov/nmc/experiment/display.action?id=1960-007B-01 | publisher = NASA Space Science Data Coordinated Archive | access-date = 2020-07-20 | archivedate = 2020-06-15 | deadurl = no }}{{PD-notice}}</ref>。

银河辐射和背景监控设备用于检测下方直径6500公里的圆形区域<ref name="25th2" />{{rp|108}}，监视在[[S波段|S波段]]（1550至3900[[赫兹|兆赫兹]]）广播的苏联防空雷达<ref name="avweek1998a" />{{rp|29, 32}}。卫星上的接收器已调到接近雷达频率，接收器的信号输出可以触发航天器上独立的[[甚高频|甚高频]]发射机。经过苏联上空期间，卫星会在接收到导弹雷达脉冲后立即向接收范围内的美国地面站转播，地面站记录信息并发送到海军实验室分析。虽然银河辐射和背景配备的是全向接收器，但多次寻找相同信号，并与卫星已经确知的位置对比，就可以推断出雷达的大致方位和准确的[[脉冲重复频率|脉冲重复频率]]。<ref name="grabnpoppy" />{{rp|4–7}}<ref name="25th2" />{{rp|108}}

[[File:Elint_info.gif|thumb]]

遥测数据通过太阳辐射监测卫星赤道上四条长63.5厘米的[[鞭状天线|鞭状天线]]传送<ref name="avweek1960a" />{{rp|76}}，科学遥测的传送频率是108兆赫兹<ref name="avweek1960a" />{{rp|78}}，这也是先锋计划使用的[[国际地球物理年|国际地球物理年]]标准频率<ref name="Vanguard">{{cite book | title = ''Vanguard – a History'' | last1 = Green | first1 = Constance | last2 = Lomask | first2 = Milton | publisher = National Aeronautics and Space Administration | location = Washington D.C. | date = 1970 | id = SP-4202 | isbn = 978-1-97353-209-5 | url = https://www.hq.nasa.gov/office/pao/History/SP-4202/begin.html | access-date = 2020-07-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303213422/http://www.hq.nasa.gov/office/pao/History/SP-4202/begin.html | archive-date = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no }}{{PD-notice}}</ref>{{rp|84, 185}}。地面指令和电子监控数据通过小型天线在139兆赫兹频率收集<ref name="grabnpoppy" />{{rp|7}}。地面获得的信息记录在磁带上并寄回海军实验室，经评估、复制，再转交位于[[马里兰州|马里兰州]][[乔治·米德堡|陆军米德堡]]（{{lang|en|Army Fort Meade}}）的[[美国国家安全局|美国国家安全局]]，以及位于[[內布拉斯加州|內布拉斯加州]][[奥马哈_(内布拉斯加州)|奥马哈]][[奥夫特空军基地|奥夫特空军基地]]（{{lang|en|Offut Air Force Base}}）的[[战略空军司令部|战略空军司令部]]分析和处理<ref name="GRAB">{{cite web | url = http://www.ncst.nrl.navy.mil/HomePage/GRAB/GRAB.html | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130215070158/http://www.ncst.nrl.navy.mil/HomePage/GRAB/GRAB.html | deadurl = yes | archive-date = 2013-02-15 | title = G R A B, Galactic RAdiation and Background,World's First Reconnaissance Satellite | publisher = U.S. Naval Research Laboratory | access-date = 2013-02-15 }}{{PD-notice}}</ref>。

与早期大部分自动航天器一样，太阳辐射监测卫星一号虽能通过旋转保持稳定<ref name="Society2010" />{{rp|300}}，但缺乏主动[[姿态控制|姿态控制]]系统，所以只能扫描整个天空，无法聚焦特定信息源<ref name="SP100" />{{rp|13}}。为了让科学家能顺利解读太阳辐射监测卫星一号探测的{{lang|en|X}}射线来源，卫星上装有真空光电管，用于确认太阳光谱撞击光度计的时间，以及阳光照射光度计的角度<ref name="SP100" />{{rp|64}}。
